  "headline": "Portfolio CTO @ Caylent",
  "summary": "Peter has been part of the AWS Community for over a decade, growing the Advanced AWS meetup (user group) in San Francisco, contributing to and created multiple open source projects, and spoke an many conferences across USA. As a day job, he is a Portfolio CTO at Caylent, looking after enterprise accounts. In his spare time, he runs the annual Answers for AWS community survey and provides strategic guidance to startups through PAS Ventures.",
